OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1780499462
OL,3,CTwo hospitalised and knife seized
OL,4,Cafter park stabbing
OL,6,FPolice have launched an investigation
OL,7,Fafter a stabbing in a Cardiff park.
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police have confirmed they
OL,10,Fare investigating a a serious assault
OL,11,Fin Lydstep Park, Gabalfa, Cardiff,
OL,12,Fwhich happened just before 7pm last
OL,13,Fnight (Sunday, May 31).
OL,15,FThe force confirmed two local boys
OL,16,Faged 16 and 17 were taken to the
OL,17,FUniversity Hospital of Wales, Cardiff,
OL,18,Fwith stab wounds.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
