CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1780499462
OL,3,CTwo hospitalised and knife seized
OL,4,Cafter park stabbing
OL,6,FTheir injuries have been described as
OL,7,Fnot life-threatening and one of the
OL,8,Fvictims has been discharged from
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FDetectives are hunting two suspects
OL,12,Fthought to have been riding a Surron
OL,13,Fbike in Lydstep Park and Gabalfa
OL,14,FAvenue around the time of the assault.
OL,16,FPolice confirmed a knife has been
OL,17,Frecovered.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
