CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1780499462
OL,3,CTwo hospitalised and knife seized
OL,4,Cafter park stabbing
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Phil Marchant,
OL,7,Ffrom South Wales Police, said: "It is
OL,8,Fvery concerning when anyone is
OL,9,Fstabbed, but the age of these two
OL,10,Fvictims is likely to worry parents and
OL,11,Fother young people in the area.
OL,13,F"We are carrying out extensive
OL,14,Fenquiries to identify those
OL,15,Fresponsible as soon as possible, and
OL,16,FCCTV will be key to the investigation.
OL,18,F"We urge witnesses or anyone with CCTV
OL,19,Fto please contact South Wales Police
OL,20,For Crimestoppers anonymously.
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
