PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1780499462
OL,3,CTwo hospitalised and knife seized
OL,4,Cafter park stabbing
OL,6,F"We are aware of the on-going concerns
OL,7,Fin the area about the illegal and anti-
OL,8,Fsocial use of e-bikes and motorbikes
OL,9,Fin the Gabalfa area.
OL,11,F"We have increased the police presence
OL,12,Fin the area, and this will continue
OL,13,Fover the coming days".
OL,15,FAnyone with any information is asked
OL,16,Fto contact South Wales Police quoting
OL,17,F2600170643.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
